{"type": "article", "id": 13381, "title": "数字电视机顶盒", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-12T07:13:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060613574327VPeSFApriUz3lw.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最近，法国设计工作室 Fuseproject 推出了一款新型的数字网络机顶盒，名叫 “Le Cube”，听起来是不是有点儿像“乐视TV”？不过他们之间没有任何关系，Fuseproject 选择和法国一家电视台 Canal+ 合作，后者主要经营付费的卫星电视业务。机顶盒看起来非常酷炫，小小的方形盒子，全黑色的外形看上去很有质感，正面有“＋”符号。他们设计了 320×240 高像素小屏幕，除了日常的需求，还专门为老人和小孩设计了更为方便的交互界面，试图有效改善看电视这一行为体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141153VgOsFZoY5HJE0v8w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60635697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141153xVSJZPGy8zpO34wM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141155FgdvacTSbMmjqUXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141155lb1oIwvWm4kDBRjf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141155Gi7hmgEaTYK3fcx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141156nw5ec8Rlqm7W4Dgh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53422983\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141156q1oQltnYaTwEKmGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37163814\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141157dPoH9FBrj0QvsGcJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141157UV5gvecboSOK8FBl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60513447\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n\n"}